cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.IT 

The paper deals with physical-layer authentication using deep neural networks, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR). The use of deep neural networks for authentication also falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves the use of channel state information (CSI) which is a concept related to network infrastructure (cs.NI) and information theory (cs.IT).
